You've never repented of your sin and trusted Jesus and Jesus alone.

45:10.048 --> 45:10.588
Hear this.

45:10.929 --> 45:11.930
See this gospel.

45:12.891 --> 45:14.913
And know this is what Jesus did for you.

45:14.993 --> 45:19.218
We pray before you walk out of here that in your heart of hearts, you will.

45:19.810 --> 45:21.413
You will surrender to Jesus Christ.

45:21.433 --> 45:22.555
You'll give your life to Him.

45:23.115 --> 45:31.169
My brothers and sisters who name the name of Christ, let's hear this familiar Bible story and let's hear this commission.

45:33.092 --> 45:41.887
And so I ask you, in 2017, how will you be inconvenienced for the sake of the gospel?

45:43.509 --> 45:46.354
What barriers, what gaps will you cross?

45:47.106 --> 46:09.296
Whether it's your own street or your side yard or the cubicle next to you or whether it is the Atlantic Ocean or the Pacific Ocean, what barriers will you cross for the sake of the gospel and what sacrifices will you make time and money in order to be a neighbor and show the radical mercy of the gospel?

46:09.736 --> 46:10.898
Will you hear the people?

46:11.010 --> 46:12.855
in Memphis and in New York.

46:12.936 --> 46:17.569
We hear the people in North Africa and in London and in Southeast Asia.

46:17.810 --> 46:23.506
Will you hear all of these people say, won't you be my neighbor?

